description:
The course is about introducing students to Sinefa's solution and how to use it to tackle network performance issues

The course is based on short videos and presentations along with simple quiz questions.

It is intended for Network Managers, Managed Services Providers and technical professionals who have a basic understanding of IP networks.
title: Course 2 - Sinefa Technical Training
instructors: Chris Siakos, John Bothe, Con Nikolouzakis, John Milionis
